Package: dream
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libfdk-aac2
Description: A software radio for AM and Digital Radio Mondiale (DRM)
 Dream is a software implementation of a Digital Radio Mondiale (DRM) receiver.
 With Dream, DRM broadcasts can be received with an SDR dongle or 
 a modified analog receiver (SW, MW, LW) and a PC with a sound card.
